      "date": "2012-06-26 13:47:43.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/751edcba-bf91-11e1-aa72-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
